called iUniverse.

00:40:22.500 --> 00:40:26.310
And that process allows the
author complete control over

00:40:26.310 --> 00:40:29.387
the creative decisions,
like cover, title, and text,

00:40:29.387 --> 00:40:30.970
but also over the
marketing decisions,

00:40:30.970 --> 00:40:33.130
which sometimes happens
with real publishers,

00:40:33.130 --> 00:40:34.645
sometimes doesn't.

00:40:34.645 --> 00:40:37.020
But that means that all the
marketing decisions from here

00:40:37.020 --> 00:40:40.314
on out are going to be my
own and those of the people

00:40:40.314 --> 00:40:41.605
who I choose to bring in on it.

