the story that I had envisioned,

00:43:20.680 --> 00:43:22.930
with far fewer details
in the beginning,

00:43:22.930 --> 00:43:25.467
but that I had originally
set out to write.

00:43:25.467 --> 00:43:26.550
SEEMA VASHI: That's great.

00:43:26.550 --> 00:43:28.800
LAUREN EPSHTEYN: Did you
